NAME
    Shell::Cap - Probe shell's capabilities

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.002 of Shell::Cap (from Perl
    distribution Shell-Cap), released on 2020-03-10.

SYNOPSIS
DESCRIPTION
FUNCTIONS
  shell_supports_pipe
    Check whether shell supports pipe syntax.

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Shell-Cap>.

SOURCE
    Source repository is at <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-Shell-Cap>.

BUGS
    Please report any bugs or feature requests on the bugtracker website
    <https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Dist/Display.html?Name=Shell-Cap>

    When submitting a bug or request, please include a test-file or a patch
    to an existing test-file that illustrates the bug or desired feature.

SEE ALSO
    The "SHELL" environment variable.

